# --- Encode/Bytes/RequestBody: raw binary content handling ---
# Convenience methods use BinaryContentHelper.FromObject() which attempts
# JSON parsing on raw binary data (PNG). Needs a separate fix to use
# BinaryContent.Create() for non-JSON byte body parameters.
